{"title":"洋浦湾之夜","authors":["夏川"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"洋浦湾之夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过刺人的野菠萝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过轻啸的椰树林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我默坐在南海之滨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩瀚的大海浪静波平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸边只有断续的虫鸣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤的渔民都已入梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洋浦湾有如一眼古井。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丛草中响起窸窣的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我转身搜寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是解放军战士在巡逻游动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的脚步是那么轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么稳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上码头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进椰林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着高度警惕的眼神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝视着他们远去的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思绪纷纭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴随着信赖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴随着崇敬！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}